  levelNumber: 18
  levelName: Ek Balam
  location: "Yucat\xE1n, Mexico"
  levelDescription: "Guarded by jaguars and gods, Ek\u2019 Balam rose as a city of
    power and artistry.\n\nEk\u2019 Balam, meaning \u201CBlack Jaguar\u201D in Yucatec
    Maya, was a powerful city in the northern Yucat\xE1n that thrived between 600\u20131000
    AD. At its height, it controlled a large territory and was known for its artistry
    and monumental architecture.\r\n\r\nThe site\u2019s centerpiece is the Acropolis,
    a massive pyramid over 30 meters tall. Within it lies the elaborately decorated
    Tomb of Ukit Kan Le\u2019k Tok\u2019, one of Ek\u2019 Balam\u2019s greatest rulers.
    Stucco sculptures of warriors, jaguars, and celestial beings adorn the temple,
    showcasing the city\u2019s unique style.\r\n\r\nEk\u2019 Balam also features
    defensive walls, ballcourts, and ceremonial plazas, reflecting its role as both
    a political stronghold and a spiritual center. Surrounded by jungle, the ruins
    remain less crowded than other Yucat\xE1n sites, offering a glimpse into a Maya
    city where artistry and power converged."
  siteImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f9368de86459d2b45ba8a3b753d691a8, type: 3}
